{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "549986ae-b1db-4f97-b272-566782722d68", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/549986ae-b1db-4f97-b272-566782722d68@3.pkg/1772597548733/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597549402", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/549986ae-b1db-4f97-b272-566782722d68@3.pkg/1772597548733/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597549402"}, "identifier": "549986ae-b1db-4f97-b272-566782722d68", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>题干中，北京、上海、兰州等城市深化改革，出台政策，不再全面禁止路边摊，此举能活跃经济，促进居民收入的增长，有利于满足人民对美好生活的需求，①③正确；社会主义市场经济体制已经建立，②错误；市场在资源配置中起决定性作用，④错误。故选B。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>改革有“温度”，社会有活力。北京、上海、兰州等城市深化改革，出台政策，不再全面禁止路边摊。北京等地解禁路边摊（ &nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n\n<p>①能活跃经济，促进居民收入的增长　</p>\n\n<p>②将会推动社会主义市场经济体制的建立　</p>\n\n<p>③有利于满足人民对美好生活的需求　</p>\n\n<p>④能发挥企业在资源配置中的决定性作用</p>\n", "title": "改革有“温度”，社会有活力。北京、上海、兰州等城市深化改革，出台政策，不再全面禁止路边摊。北京等地解禁路边摊（   ）①能活跃经济，促进居民收入的增长　②将会推动社会主义市场经济体制的建立　③有利于满足人民对美好生活的需求　④能发挥企业在资源配置中的决定性作用", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/549986ae-b1db-4f97-b272-566782722d68@3.pkg/item.json?v=1754670317564", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options"